{"tid":1778664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大國會成立委員會檢視與中國關係","createTime":"2019-12-11T06:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T10:10:09.000Z","uid":92301,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"94122df017aae84c6670d082e58d11549997c71a","tid":1778664,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"加拿大國會以171票贊成、148票反對，通過成立特別委員會，檢視與中國的關係。提出議案的保守黨一直批評總理杜魯多對中國過於軟弱，建議成立12人的委員會，將會召開聽證會，全面檢視加中關係，首次會議將於明年一月舉行。保守黨指特別委員會將揭示杜魯多，在面對中國時保障加方利益的失敗。杜魯多暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大早前應美方要求，拘捕中國電訊設備製造商華為副董事長孟晚舟；中方其後羈押加拿大前外交官康明凱及商人邁克爾斯帕弗，兩國關係因而變得緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1233591&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1233591%26csid%3D261_341&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=772fc68b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1233591&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"eba6dad6a70dc0d18d82c17adf4513fe29777af0","tid":1778664,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美加議員講對華政策，<br />\n響task2 急要人</span></span><br />\n適逢人權日，世界上人權被打壓嘅國家或地區唔少，當然其中一個亮點係打壓緊香港同新疆嘅中國！<br />\n<br />\n多國政要發推文關注中國打壓人權嘅情況，精選推文遍布task 1 &amp; 2，大家快啲去回應啦！<br />\n<br />\n記得落hashtag #humanrights #HumanRightsDay 呀～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=81940ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"a0e5a3179fbc884b1596dd33b11c6595a7029a59","tid":1778664,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"reply